#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; is an easy to use personal information manager (<acronym>PIM</"
"acronym>). You can write journal entries, schedule appointments, events, and "
"to-dos. &korganizer; will remind you about pending tasks, and help you keep "
"your schedule."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; on hõlpsasti kasutatav isikliku info haldur (<acronym>PIM</"
"acronym>, inglise keeles <quote>personal information manager</quote>). Selle "
"abil saab panna kirja päevikut ning ajastada kohtumisi, sündmusi ja "
"ülesandeid. &korganizer; meenutab sulle eesseisvaid ülesandeid ja aitab "
"ajakava korras hoida."

