#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Groupware Communication"
msgstr "Grupitöö kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to automatically send emails when creating, updating or "
"deleting events or to-dos which involve others. This email can be an "
"invitation to attendees of an event you created, a cancellation of an event "
"you created, an answer or an update on your invitation status, an event "
"change request, &etc; Check this option if you want to use the groupware "
"functionality (&eg; Configuring &kontact; as a &kde; <guilabel>Kolab</"
"guilabel> client)."
msgstr ""
"Selle märkimisel saadetakse automaatselt kirjad sündmuste või ülesannete "
"loomisel, uuendamisel või kustutamisel, mis hõlmavad ka teisi isikuid. Kiri "
"võib olla kutse vastloodud sündmuse osalejatele, loodud sündmuse "
"katkestamise teade, vastus kutsele või oma staatuse uuendamine, soov "
"sündmust muuta &etc; Lülita see sisse, kui soovid kasutada grupitöö "
"võimalusi (nt. seadistada &kontact;i &kde; <guilabel>Kolab</guilabel>i "
"kliendiks)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Send copy to owner when mailing events"
msgstr "Sündmuste e-postiga edastamisel saadetakse koopia ka omanikule"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you check the <guilabel>Send copy to owner when mailing events</"
"guilabel> box, you will get a copy of all email messages that &korganizer; "
"sends at your request to the event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgid ära kasti <guilabel>Sündmuste e-postiga edastamisel saadetakse "
"koopia ka omanikule</guilabel>, saadetakse sulle koopia kõigist meilidest, "
"mida &korganizer; sinu soovil sündmuste osalistele saadab."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mail transport"
msgstr "Kirjade saatmise viis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose which type of mail transport you would like to use. You "
"can either use &kmail; or the &Sendmail; command (which must be installed on "
"your system in order to work)."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab valida, millist e-posti klienti kasutada. Selleks võib olla "
"näiteks &kmail; või &Sendmail; (mis peab mõistagi olema süsteemi "
"paigaldatud)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish"
msgstr "Avaldamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By publishing your free/busy information, you allow others to take your busy "
"time schedule into account when inviting you to an event."
msgstr ""
"Oma vaba/hõivatud infot avaldades annad teistele võimaluse arvestada sinu "
"hõivatud aegade kava kohtumisi planeerides, kuhu neil on mõttes ka sind "
"kutsuda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish free/busy information automatically"
msgstr "Vaba/hõivatud info automaatne avaldamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable this option if you wish your Free/Busy information to be uploaded "
"automatically. Note that you may skip this option and choose to mail or "
"upload your Free/Busy information via the <guilabel>Schedule</guilabel> menu "
"of &korganizer;."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel saad lasta oma vaba/hõivatud info automaatselt avaldada. Pane "
"tähele, et sa võid selle ka valimata jätta ning saata oma vaba/hõivatud info "
"e-postiga või võrku laadida &korganizer;i menüü <guilabel>Ajaplaneerija</"
"guilabel> käskudega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your application is setup to work as a <guilabel>&kde; Kolab client</"
"guilabel>, this is not required. The <guilabel>Kolab2</guilabel> server can "
"take care of publishing your Free/Busy information and manage the access to "
"it from other users."
msgstr ""
"Kui sinu rakendus töötab <guilabel>&kde; Kolabi kliendina</guilabel>, ei ole "
"see vajalik. <guilabel>Kolab2</guilabel> server hoolitseb ise sinu vaba/"
"hõivatud info avaldamise eest ja tagab teistele kasutajatele sellele "
"ligipääsu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum time between uploads (in minutes)"
msgstr "Üleslaadimiste min. ajavahe (minutites)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to publish your information automatically, you can configure "
"the interval of time in minutes between each upload."
msgstr ""
"Kui otsustad oma infot automaatselt avaldada, saad määrata ka üleslaadimiste "
"vahele jääva intervalli minutites."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Publish (default 60) days of free/busy information"
msgstr "Avaldatakse (vaikimisi 60) päeva vaba/hõivatud info"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the number of calendar days you wish to be published and available "
"to others"
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata, mitme kalendripäeva info avaldatakse ja on kättesaadav "
"teistele."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2573 index.docbook:2638
#, no-c-format
msgid "Server &URL;"
msgstr "Serveri &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the &URL; for the server on which your Free/Busy information will be "
"published. Ask the server administrator for this information."
msgstr ""
"Kirjuta siia serveri &URL;, kus sinu vaba/hõivatud info avaldada. Vajaduse "
"korral küsi seda serveri administraatorilt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kolab2 server example: <userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/freebusy/joe@kolab2."
"com.ifb</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Kolab2 serveri näide: <userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/freebusy/juhan@kolab2."
"com.ifb</userinput>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2582 index.docbook:2647
#, no-c-format
msgid "Username"
msgstr "Kasutajanimi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the login information relative to your account on the server"
msgstr "Kirjuta siia sinu kontot serveris puudutav info."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kolab2 server specificity: your registered UID (Unique IDentifier), by "
"default, would be similar to your email address on the Kolab2 server but it "
"may be different. In this case enter your UID. Ask the server administrator "
"about your UID if you do not know it."
msgstr ""
"Kolab2 serveri eriomadused: sinu registreeritud UID (Unikaalne "
"IDentifikaator). Vaikimisi peaks see olema sama sinu e-posti aadressiga "
"Kolab2 serveris, kuid võib ka sellest erineda. Viimasel juhul kirjutagi siia "
"oma UID. Kui sa seda ei tea, küsi seda serveri administraatori käest."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2591 index.docbook:2654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password"
msgstr "Parool"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2592 index.docbook:2655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter your password (server login password) here."
msgstr "Kirjuta siia oma parool (serverisse siselogimiseks)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2596 index.docbook:2660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember password"
msgstr "Parool jäetakse meelde"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want &korganizer; to remember your password and "
"skip asking you each time it uploads your Free/Busy information."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel jätab &korganizer; sinu parooli meelde ega küsi seda "
"edaspidi, kui vaba/hõivatud infot üles laadid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2600 index.docbook:2663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not recommended to store your password in the configuration file for "
"security reasons."
msgstr ""
"Turvakaalutlustel ei ole soovitatav oma parooli seadistustefailis salvestada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2609
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieve"
msgstr "Tõmbamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By retrieving other people's free/busy information, you can take their busy "
"time schedule into account when inviting them to an event."
msgstr ""
"Teiste vaba/hõivatud infot hankides saad arvestada nende hõivatud aegade "
"kava kohtumisi planeerides, kuhu kavatsed teisi kutsuda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieve other people's free/busy information automatically"
msgstr "Teiste inimeste vaba/hõivatud info automaatne tõmbamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2620
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automate the process for retrieving other users free/busy time. Fill in the "
"server information section below to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Sellega saab teiste isikute vaba/hõivatud info tõmbamise automatiseerida. "
"Selle kasutamiseks täida allpool vajalikud serveri info väljad."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:2626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use full email address for retrieval"
msgstr "Hankimisel kasutatakse täielikku e-posti aadressi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting lets you change the name of the file which will be fetched from "
"the server. If you check this option, it will download a free/busy file "
"called <userinput>user@domain.ifb</userinput>, else it will fetch "
"<userinput>user.ifb</userinput>. Ask the server administrator if you are not "
"sure about how to configure this option."
msgstr ""
"Sellega saab muuta faili nime, mida serverist tõmmatakse. Selle märkimisel "
"tõmmatakse vaba/hõivatud info fail nimetusega <userinput>kasutaja@domeen."
"ifb</userinput>, muidu aga <userinput>kasutaja.ifb</userinput>. Kui sa ei "
"ole väga kindel, küsi serveri administraatorilt, kuidas peaks talitama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Kolab2 server specificity:</guilabel> If you are configuring "
"&korganizer; as a component to a <guilabel>&kde; Kolab client (&kontact;/"
"Kolab)</guilabel> you have to check this option."
msgstr ""
"Kolab2 serveri eriomadused: kui oled määranud &korganizer;i <guilabel>&kde; "
"Kolabi kliendi (&kontact;/Kolab)</guilabel> komponendiks, tuleb sul see "
"sisse lülitada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the &URL; for the server from which your Free/Busy information will be "
"fetched. Ask the server administrator for this information."
msgstr ""
"Kirjuta siia serveri &URL;, kust vaba/hõivatud info tõmmata. Vajaduse korral "
"küsi seda serveri administraatorilt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Kolab2 server example: </guilabel><userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/"
"freebusy/</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kolab2 serveri näide: </guilabel><userinput>webdavs://kolab2.com/"
"freebusy/</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the login information relative to your account on the server."
msgstr "Kirjuta siia sinu kontot serveris puudutav info."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this option if you want &korganizer; to remember your password and "
"skip asking you each time it fetches the free/busy files."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel jätab &korganizer; sinu parooli meelde ega küsi seda "
"edaspidi, kui vaba/hõivatud info faile tõmbad."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2673 index.docbook:2694
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Pluginad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about configuring plugins, please refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"plugins-chapter\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib seadistamispluginatest <xref linkend=\"plugins-chapter\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Pages"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to add your own &GUI; Elements to store your own values "
"into &korganizer;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create your elements as described in <guilabel>How does this work?</guilabel>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer; provides you with the possibility of extending the application "
"with plugins."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer; võimaldab põhirakenduse võimalusi märgatavalt laiendada "
"pluginate abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2700
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugins can be configured under the &korganizer; main configuration "
"dialog. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Configure &korganizer;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and click the "
"<guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> icon on the icon list sidebar of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pluginaid saab seadistada &korganizer;i peamises seadistustedialoogis. Vali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem> &korganizer;i "
"seadistamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ja klõpsa dialoogi ikooniribal "
"ikoonile <guilabel>Pluginad</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2708
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Plugins"
msgstr "Saadaolevad pluginad"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date Numbers Plugin for Calendars"
msgstr "Kuupäevanumbrite plugin kalendritele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin adds the number of the day in the year to the Agenda view. For "
"instance, February 1 is day number 32."
msgstr ""
"See plugin lisab päevakavavaates päevadele nende järjekorranumbri aastas. "
"Nii on näiteks 1. veebruar 32. päev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia 'This Day in History' Plugin"
msgstr "Wikipedia 'täna ajaloos' plugin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin provides links to Wikipedia's <quote>This Day in History</quote> "
"pages."
msgstr ""
"See plugin pakub linke Wikipedia <quote>Täna ajaloos</quote> lehekülgedele."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia Picture of the Day Plugin for Calendars"
msgstr "Wikipedia päevapildi plugin kalendritele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2727
#, no-c-format
msgid "This plugin provides the Wikipedia <quote>Picture of the Day</quote>."
msgstr "See plugin võimaldab näha Wikipedia <quote>päevapilti</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jewish Calendar Plugin"
msgstr "Juudi kalendri plugin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2734
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This plugin provides Jewish calendar dates in addition to the Gregorian "
#| "calendar dates. In the configuration dialog of the plugin, you can choose "
#| "if you want to display Israeli holidays, weekly prasha, day of Omer and/"
#| "or Chol HaMoed."
msgid ""
"This plugin provides Jewish calendar dates in addition to the Gregorian "
"calendar dates. In the configuration dialog of the plugin, you can choose if "
"you want to display Israeli holidays, weekly Parsha, day of Omer and/or Chol "
"HaMoed."
msgstr ""
"See plugin võimaldab lisaks Gregoriuse kalendri kuupäevadele kasutada ka "
"juudi kalendri päevi. Plugina seadistustedialoogis saab valida, kas lasta "
"esitada Iisraeli pühasid, parsha-nädalates või Omeri või Chol HaMoedi "
"päevades."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2747
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "Seletused"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2750
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Menüüd"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &korganizer; starts, the main &korganizer; window appears. The window "
"has several components: a menubar, a toolbar, a month calendar, a main panel "
"with the current <quote>view</quote> of events, and a to-do list."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer;i käivitamisel ilmub &korganizer;i peaaken. See koosneb mitmest "
"osast: menüüriba, tööriistariba, kuukalender, peapaneel sündmuste käesoleva "
"<quote>vaatega</quote> ja ülesannete nimekiri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menus provide access to all the common operations that can be performed "
"with the calendar, including saving, loading, adding and deleting events, to-"
"dos and journal entries, printing and more."
msgstr ""
"Menüüd pakuvad võimaluse kasutada kõiki toiminguid, mida saab ette võtta "
"kalendriga, sealhulgas sündmuste, ülesannete ja päevikukirjete salvestamine, "
"avamine, lisamine ja kustutamine, trükkimine ja nii edasi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that when using &korganizer; as the calendar component of "
"&kontact;, the menus differ from the stand alone application."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et &korganizer;i kasutamisel &kontact;i kalendrikomponendina on "
"menüüd mõnevõrra teistsugused."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2765
#, no-c-format
msgid "File"
msgstr "Fail"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu provides access to functions involving the "
"entire calendar."
msgstr ""
"Menüü <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> võimaldab kasutada kogu kalendrit hõlmavaid "
"toiminguid."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ava</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a file dialog allowing you to select a new vCalendar or "
"iCalendar file to load.</action> If you have made changes to the current "
"calendar, you will be given the option of saving them before loading a new "
"one."
msgstr ""
"<action>Avab failidialoogi, kus saab valida avamiseks uue vCalendar või "
"iCalendar faili.</action> Kui oled teinud parajasti avatud kalendrisse "
"muutusi, küsitakse sinu käest, kas soovid need enne uue kalendri avamist "
"salvestada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this, please refer to <xref linkend=\"managing-"
"import-export\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"managing-import-export\"/"
">."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Trüki</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> or click the <guilabel>Print</"
"guilabel> icon to <action>print the current calendar</action>. You can "
"specify the range of dates to be printed (either manually or with the "
"Calendar Widget) and the Print Style (Day, Week, Month or To-dos and "
"Journal)."
msgstr ""
"Vali menüükäsk <guimenuitem>Trüki</guimenuitem> või klõpsa ikoonile "
"<guilabel>Trüki</guilabel>, kui tahad <action>parajasti avatud kalendri "
"välja trükkida</action>. Võimalik on määrata trükitavate kuupäevade vahemik "
"(kas käsitsi või kalendrividinaga) ning vaate tüüp (päev, kuu, nädal või "
"ülesanne ja päevik)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2809
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Trükkimise eelvaatlus</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose <guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem> or click the "
"<guiicon>Print Preview</guiicon> icon, <action>the current calendar will be "
"printed on your screen, instead of on your printer</action>. Use this "
"feature to check if the printout will be correct before you start printing."
msgstr ""
"Kui valida <guimenuitem>Trükkimise eelvaatlust</guimenuitem> või klõpsata "
"ikoonile <guiicon>Trükkimise eelvaatlus</guiicon>, <action>nii-öelda "
"trükitakse aktiivne kalender ekraanil, mitte aga ei saadeta printerisse</"
"action>. Nii saab juba enne tegelikku trükkimist kontrollida, kas kõik on "
"ikka õigesti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify the range of dates to be printed (either manually or with "
"the Calendar Widget) and the View Type (Day, Week, Month or To-do)."
msgstr ""
"Võimalik on määrata trükitavate kuupäevade vahemik (kas käsitsi või "
"kalendrividinaga) ning vaate tüüp (päev, kuu, nädal või ülesanne)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Import "
"Calendar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Impordi "
"kalender</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a different iCalendar or vCalendar file somewhere, and you would "
"like to <action>merge its contents into your own calendar, add as a new "
"resource or open it as a new window</action>, choose this menu item. A good "
"time to do this would be if you received a vCalendar with a few entries via "
"email, for instance."
msgstr ""
"Kui sul on mõni iCalendar või vCalendar fail ja sa soovid <action>liita "
"selle sisu oma praeguse kalendriga, lisada selle uue ressursina või avada "
"uues aknas</action>, kasuta just seda võimalust. Näiteks on seda mõttekas "
"teha juhul, kui oled saanud e-postiga mõne uue vCalendar faili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-import\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"managing-import\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"as iCalendar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Eksport</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ekspordi iCalendarina</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2845
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action will export all your active events, to-dos and journal entries "
"(independent of to which resource they belong) as a new iCalendar file."
msgstr ""
"See toiming ekspordib kõik aktiivsed sündmused, ülesanded ja päevikukirjed "
"(sõltumata sellest, millisele ressursile need kuuluvad) uue iCalendar "
"failina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-export\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"managing-export\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2854
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Archive Old Entries...</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Archive Old Incidences...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Arhiveeri vanad kirjed...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2858
#, no-c-format
msgid "From time to time you should delete your old events."
msgstr "Aegajalt võib olla mõttekas vanu kirjeid kustutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2860 index.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"managing-purge-archive\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"managing-purge-archive\"/"
">."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Purge Completed To-dos</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kustuta lõpetatud ülesanded</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action will remove all the completed to-dos from your active calendar."
msgstr "See toiming eemaldab aktiivsest kalendrist kõik lõpetatud ülesanded."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> or click the <guiicon>Quit</"
"guiicon> icon, <action>the current calendar window will quit, prompting you "
"to save if the current calendar has been modified but not yet saved.</action>"
msgstr ""
"Menüükäsk <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem> või klõps ikoonile "
"<guiicon>Välju</guiicon> <action>sulgeb aktiivse kalendriakna, küsides "
"juhul, kui sellesse on tehtud muudatusi, mida ei ole salvestatud, kas soovid "
"need salvestada</action>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has no effect on other calendar windows which may be opened. You have "
"to quit each calendar window individually."
msgstr ""
"See käsk ei mõjuta ülejäänud avatud kalendriaknaid. Iga aken tuleb eraldi "
"sulgeda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Redigeerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> menu you can edit and search events and "
"to-dos."
msgstr ""
"Menüü <guilabel>Redigeerimine</guilabel> võimaldab muuta ja otsida sündmusi "
"ja ülesandeid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>, and "
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> menu items behave in the same fashion as in "
"other &kde; applications. With the <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem> menu item "
"you can find events and to-dos across the current calendar."
msgstr ""
"Käsud <guimenuitem>Lõika</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</guimenuitem> "
"ja <guimenuitem>Aseta</guimenuitem> toimivad sarnaselt muudele &kde; "
"rakendustele. Käsuga <guimenuitem>Otsi</guimenuitem> saab leida sündmusi ja "
"ülesandeid parajasti aktiivses kalendris."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Võta tagasi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undo the latest action</action>, or in other words, return the "
"calendar to the state it was immediately before the latest action."
msgstr ""
"<action>Võtab tagasi viimase toimingu</action> ehk viib kalendri tagasi "
"olekusse, mis valitses enne viimast toimingut."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Redo</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu> Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tee "
"uuesti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Redo the latest action</action>, or in other words, return the "
"calendar to the state it was immediately before the latest undo."
msgstr ""
"<action>Sooritab uuesti viimase toimingu</action> ehk viib kalendri tagasi "
"olekusse, mis valitses enne viimast tagasivõtmist."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lõika</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Cuts the currently selected event(s) to the clipboard, removing them from "
"your calendar."
msgstr ""
"Lõikab parajasti valitud elemendi(d) lõikepuhvrisse, eemaldades selle/need "
"ühtlasi kalendrist."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopeeri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the currently selected item(s) to the clipboard, but leaving them "
"untouched."
msgstr ""
"Kopeerib parajasti valitud elemendi(d) lõikepuhvrisse, jättes selle/need "
"samas alles ka kalendrisse."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Aseta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2974
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem> <action>inserts the contents of the "
"clipboard into your calendar</action>. The clipboard must contain a valid "
"vCalendar or iCalendar item, provided either by a previous Cut/Copy "
"operation or from a selection made outside of &korganizer;. You will be "
"warned if the contents of the clipboard cannot be understood."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Aseta</guimenuitem> <action>lisab lõikepuhvri sisu kalendrisse</"
"action>. Lõikepuhver peab sisaldama sobivat vCalendari või iCalendari "
"elementi, mille eelduseks on varasem lõikamis- või kopeerimiskäsk või "
"valimine väljaspool &korganizer;it. Kui lõikepuhvri sisu osutub "
"arusaamatuks, ilmub veateade."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, you can safely use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> hotkeys to copy text data from any outside application to a "
"&korganizer; Edit Event window and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Siiski saab kiirklahve <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo> ja <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> "
"kasutada ka andmete kopeerimiseks mõnest muust rakendusest &korganizer;i "
"sündmuse muutmise dialoogi või vastupidi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2988
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kustuta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:2992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the currently selected item(s), removing them from your calendar."
msgstr ""
"Kustutab parajasti valitud elemendi(d), eemaldades selle/need ühtlasi "
"kalendrist."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu> Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Otsi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3006
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Choose <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
#| "or click the <guiicon>Find</guiicon> icon to <action>find events, to-dos "
#| "and journal entries according to their title, description, and/or "
#| "categories</action>."
msgid ""
"Choose <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> or "
"click the <guiicon>Find</guiicon> icon to <action>find events, to-dos and "
"journal entries according to their summary, description, and/or tags</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Vali menüükäsk <guimenuitem>Otsi</guimenuitem> (menüüs "
"<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu>) või klõpsa ikoonile <guiicon>Otsi</"
"guiicon>, et <action>leida sündmus, ülesanne või päevikukirje vastavalt "
"selle tiitlile, kirjeldusele ja/või kategooriale</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"search-view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"search-view\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3019
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Vaade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several different <quote>views</quote> available for displaying "
"your events, to-dos and journal entries. &korganizer; is smart enough to "
"remember in between sessions what the last active view was, and the next "
"time it is started, it will display that view."
msgstr ""
"Sündmuste, ülesannete ja päevikukirjete vaatamiseks on võimalik kasutada "
"mitmeid <quote>vaateid</quote>. &korganizer; suudab ka seansside vahel "
"meelde jätta, millist vaadet sa viimati kasutasid ning rakenduse uuel "
"käivitamisel just selle avada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, each view will provide a way of displaying your journal entries, "
"to-dos and events, constrained to a particular time period or style of "
"display. Click any item to select it for further action. <mousebutton>Right</"
"mousebutton> click an item to bring up a menu with options such as "
"<guimenuitem>Edit</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>, and so "
"on. You can also use the <guimenu>Action</guimenu> menu to perform similar "
"operations."
msgstr ""
"Üldiselt pakub iga vaade võimaluse näha päevikukirjeid, ülesandeid ja "
"sündmusi kas teatud konkreetsel ajavahemikul või teatud konkreetsel kujul. "
"Klõpsa edasise toimingu sooritamiseks suvalisel elemendil. Klõps hiire "
"<mousebutton>parema</mousebutton> nupuga elemendil avab menüü võimalustega "
"seda <guimenuitem>muuta</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>kustutada</guimenuitem> "
"ja nii edasi. Toimingu sooritamiseks võib kasutada ka <guimenu>toimingute</"
"guimenu> menüüd."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3038
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Agenda</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Päevakavavaade</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Agenda view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse päevakavavaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3044 index.docbook:3211 index.docbook:3224 index.docbook:3240
#: index.docbook:3255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"agenda-view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"agenda-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3051
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Month View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kuuvaade</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Month view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse kuuvaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"month-view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"month-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3064
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Timeline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ajateljevaade</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3068
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Timeline view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse ajateljevaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"timeline-view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"timeline-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3078
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>To-do List</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ülesannete nimekiri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the To-do List view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse ülesannete nimekirja vaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"todo-"
"view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"todo-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3090
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Event List</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Vaade</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sündmuste nimekiri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the list view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse nimekirjavaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3095
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend=\"list-"
"view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"list-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> View</guimenu><guimenuitem>What's Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu> Vaade</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mis järgmiseks?</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the what's next view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse vaate 'Mis järgmiseks?'."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This view displays your next events and to-dos. Events and to-dos are "
"displayed one per line."
msgstr ""
"See vaade näitab sinu järgmisi sündmusi ja ülesandeid. Igale sündmusele ja "
"ülesandele on eraldatud omaette rida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"whatsnext-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"whatsnext-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Journal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Päevik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Journal view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse päevikuvaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about this action, please refer to <xref linkend="
"\"journal-view\"/>."
msgstr "Täpsemalt räägib sellest toimingust <xref linkend=\"journal-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Värskenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updates or refreshes the currently displayed view."
msgstr "Uuendab või värskendab parajasti avatud vaadet."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Suurendus</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this submenu to adjust the current view to show more or less data."
msgstr ""
"Selle alammenüüga saab kohandada aktiivset vaadet, et näha rohkem või vähem "
"andmeid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the Agenda view (Day(s) or Week view), you can use the zoom actions to "
"show more or less days (<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>In Horizontally</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice> "
"<guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Out Horizontally</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>), or more or less hours in the day "
"(<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>In Vertically</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Zoom</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Out Vertically</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"Päevakavavaates (päev, päevad või nädal) saab suurendustoimingutega lasta "
"näidata rohkem või vähem päevi (<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Suurendus</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Suurenda rõhtsalt</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ja "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu>Suurendus</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vähenda "
"rõhtsalt</guimenuitem></menuchoice>) või rohkem või vähem tunde päevas "
"(<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Suurendus</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Suurenda "
"püstiselt</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ja <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Suurendus</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vähenda püstiselt</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Filter</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu offers access to the filters already created using the <link "
"linkend=\"menu-settings-edit-filters\"><guilabel>Edit Calendar Filters</"
"guilabel></link> dialog. <action>Select on this submenu the filter that will "
"be used in &korganizer; view</action>. If you do not want to use a filter, "
"choose <guilabel>No filter</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"See alammenüü võimaldab kasutada filtreid, mille oled loonud dialoogiga "
"<link linkend=\"menu-settings-edit-filters\"><guilabel>Kalendri filtrite "
"redigeerimine</guilabel></link>. <action>Vali alammenüüs filter, mida soovid "
"kasutada &korganizer;i vaates.</action>. Kui sa filtreid kasutada ei soovi, "
"vali <guilabel>Filter puudub</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:3169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Go</title>"
msgstr "<title>Liikumine</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about browsing &korganizer; views, please refer to "
"<xref linkend=\"description-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt räägib liikumisest &korganizer;i vaadetes <xref linkend="
"\"description-view\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Backward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tagasi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous day, week or month, depending on the view."
msgstr "Liigub sõltuvalt vaatest eelmisele päevale, nädalale või kuule."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3187
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edasi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next day, week, or month, depending on the view."
msgstr "Liigub sõltuvalt vaatest järgmisele päevale, nädalale või kuule."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3197
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>To Today</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tänasele</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the period of time that includes the current day."
msgstr "Liigub ajavahemikule, mis hõlmab tänast päeva."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Day</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Päev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Day view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse päevavaate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next x Days</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Järgmised x päeva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the display to the Next x Day view, where x is defined in "
"&korganizer; main configuration."
msgstr ""
"Lülitab sisse järgmise x päeva vaate, kus x on määratud &korganizer;i "
"põhiseadistuses."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Work Week</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Töönädal</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Work Week view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse töönädala vaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the same as the Week view, except only the working days of the week "
"are shown."
msgstr ""
"See on samasugune nagu nädalavaade, ainult et näidatakse vaid tööpäevi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:3247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu> Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Week</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nädal</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:3251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the display to the Week view."
msgstr "Lülitab sisse nädalavaate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3252
